 - you never know when they'll come in hand throughout the story!<br></li><li>Build your relationship by choosing the right dialogue options...and see how everything unfurls if you choose wrongly.<br></li><li>Create a daily schedule to use your time wisely before it runs out!<br></li><li>Look forward to various exciting story endings.</li></ul>",
